abstract: InBev insisted on Thursday its $52 billion takeover of Anheuser-Busch was on track after third-quarter results slightly exceeded expectations despite rocketing costs.
lead_paragraph: InBev insisted on Thursday its $52 billion takeover of Anheuser-Busch was on track after third-quarter results slightly exceeded expectations despite rocketing costs.

headline.main: InBev Says Anheuser Deal Is a Go, as Results Beat Forecasts
